title: Keema Naan Recipe | The Best Stuffed Naan Recipe
description:
This Keema Naan Recipe is so packed with flavor your taste buds wont believe it. Keema naan is amazing and especially when you start by making your own spice mixture. I hope you love this keema naan recipe as much as I did.

INGREDIENTS: 1 recipe naan dough (link in video)
for the spice mix:
3/4 TBSP coriander seed
3/4 TBSP cumin seed
3/4 TBSP mustard seed
1/2 TBSP chili powder
1/2 TBSP garam masala
1/2 TBSP black pepper

for the lamb mix:
1 lb fatty ground lamb
1/2 large onion diced
1 thumb sized ginger diced
2 large garlic cloves diced
1/3 fresno chili diced
5 TBSP tomato paste
3/4 TBSP maldon salt
2 slices muenster cheese
